I recently starting playing with the Rawr application, and I was trying to figure out why Dodge and Parry seem to have almost no value on the ProtWarr score.

For example: Rune of Repulsion (parry) only has 60.06, and Furnace Stone only has 44.25 ProWarr value.  Was there a setting that I had to change from the default settings?
